1
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:20,760
Hit him!

2
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:30,400
Hit him! Hit him! Hit him!

3
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:46,320
Come on! Come on! Come on!

4
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:08,600
Mr. Gao, Wu Qiang introduced me.

5
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,120
The kid from Dayang Village.

6
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,120
What's your name?

7
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:17,570
My name is Yang Gang.

8
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,000
Yang Gang.

9
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,220
What do you want to talk about?

10
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:29,200
I... I have some gold.

11
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,079
I was hoping you'd buy it.

12
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,360
Buy gold?

13
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,960
I don't know anything about buying gold or silver.

14
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,840
I only like watching boxing matches.

15
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,380
Go up there and fight a few rounds.

16
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,440
If you win,

17
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:49,920
then we can talk about whatever you said,

18
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:52,400
about gold or silver or whatever.

19
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:04,880
Come on! Come on! Come on!

20
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:12,520
Come on, Daxiong!

21
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:32,520
Treating cancer is a bottomless pit.

22
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,280
You have to pay the interest today.

23
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,880
The three of you don't need to come to work anymore.

24
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,920
It's only because we're from the same hometown

25
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,450
that I let you delay paying the medical bills.

26
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:03,320
Come on! Come on!

27
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,880
After careful discussion by the Group,

28
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:20,320
here is the list of miners contracted by Shanshui Group.

29
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,279
Zhao Weiguo.

30
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,680
Ye Zicheng.

31
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,200
Yu Lei.

32
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,000
Wang Zhongyuan.

33
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,680
Li Fugui.

34
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,040
Liu Dagang.

35
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,440
Li Tian.

36
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:31,960
Wang Wenqiang.

37
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,200
That concludes the list.

38
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:37,040
Thank you for supporting Shanshui Group's restructuring. That is all.

39
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,040
Why isn't my name there?

40
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,840
Yeah.

41
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,520
Where is the satisfactory answer you promised?

42
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,040
Isn't this just laying us off?

43
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,880
You're laying us off, aren't you?

44
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,680
Yeah. This is a layoff.

45
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,520
Our mine doesn't need that many miners right now.

46
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,400
But for those who weren't selected,

47
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,720
we will figure something out.

48
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,360
More excuses! Liar!

49
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,480
The Group won't give up on anyone.

50
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,640
Please, you must trust us.

51
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,480
Liar! Not a word of truth!

52
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,040
Young men with no work,

53
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,840
forced to steal or rob.

54
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,280
It's all because of your Shanshui Group

55
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,960
that Dayang Village has become like this.

56
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:05,640
Get out!

57
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,280
Get out! Get out of Dayang Village!

58
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,080
Get out.

59
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:12,400
Get out of Dayang Village!

60
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,080
Get out.

61
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,120
Get out.

62
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,640
Get out.

63
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,680
Mr. Gao, I won.

64
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,320
Too bad, I lost.

65
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,000
I bet on Daxiong.

66
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:37,890
What do you mean?

67
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:42,240
I don't do business with people from Dayang Village.

68
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,640
Gao Shan.

69
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,780
Wait, Brother.

70
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,480
How did you get hurt like this?

71
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,880
You weren't beaten by Gao Shan's men, were you?

72
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,640
I'm fine.

73
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,900
You two sit down first.

74
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:11,000
I went to see Gao Shan today.

75
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,760
He said that only our Dayang Village's ore,

76
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,010
he won't accept.

77
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,260
Gao Shan is originally from Dayang Village.

78
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,160
He stopped working with us a long time ago.

79
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,520
Back then, he was betrayed by Xiao Tianman

80
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,480
and left town.

81
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:25,280
So he holds a grudge against us.

82
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:25,920
Right.

83
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:29,160
So I think that must be the reason.

84
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:34,600
I want to see if we can use this matter

85
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,090
to find a breakthrough.

86
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,320
Who is it?

87
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,480
I...

88
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,159
I'm going out.

89
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,970
The villagers are causing trouble again.

90
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,480
I can't help you.

91
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:15,060
Aren't you my employee representative?

92
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,320
But you lied to me.

93
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:20,000
You used me to complete the restructuring.

94
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,400
Talking to me about new frameworks,

95
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,330
new structures.

96
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:23,900
And the result?

97
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,370
Many villagers still got laid off.

98
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,480
Don't speak English to me. I don't understand.

99
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,080
Management Buyout.

100
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,960
Management Buyout.

101
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,480
What about the ordinary people?

102
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,880
Isn't that just like before?

103
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,000
Inefficient.

104
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,159
Besides, after the reform,

105
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:40,200
we rely more on mechanized production.

106
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,960
We don't need that many workers.

107
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:42,760
Efficiency.

108
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,600
People like you only care about efficiency.

109
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,640
Only profit.

110
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,440
You don't see people like us at all.

111
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,360
And you don't care.

112
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,360
Without profit,

113
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,159
how can Shanshui Group survive?

114
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:54,370
Our group has many employees who need to survive too.

115
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:55,960
Aren't they human?

116
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,360
I finally get it.

117
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:01,080
You're no different from Xiao Tianman.

118
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,600
He used the old system to rob the villagers.

119
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,600
Miss Situ,

120
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:08,360
you use the new system to keep robbing them.

121
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:39,880
Hello.

122
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,760
Why is the line so long?

123
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:43,490
Is this the township hospital?

124
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,960
Hospital? This is just a small clinic.

125
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,450
Why not go to a big hospital?

126
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:54,320
Shanshui Group carried out reforms.

127
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:57,240
My whole family got laid off.

128
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,280
How can we afford a big hospital?

129
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,800
Shanshui Group...

130
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:04,730
Didn't they come to help Dayang Village develop?

131
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:05,680
Develop?

132
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,600
Development that leaves people starving?

133
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,260
Forcing people to sell blood?

134
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:12,880
If I see anyone from Shanshui Group, I'll beat them up.

135
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:28,920
Shanshui Group, get out of Dayang Village!

136
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:29,520
Come out!

137
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,780
Quiet down, everyone.

138
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,240
Quiet down.

139
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,080
Listen to me.

140
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:39,280
Shansui Group acquired Dayang Village Mine

141
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,960
to implement new systems,

142
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,760
new ideas, and new technologies

143
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,840
to better develop the mine.

144
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,000
Better develop?

145
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,080
Better development means laying us off.

146
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,480
Just because we're uneducated,

147
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,400
we're easy to push around?

148
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,760
You made all the money,

149
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,240
while we keep getting poorer. Why?

150
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,300
Good question.

151
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,960
That is the mistake I made.

152
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,800
I thought that for development

153
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:02,760
and efficiency,

154
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,620
some things could be sacrificed.

155
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,040
But I was wrong.

156
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:10,200
I confused the means with the end.

157
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,880
Efficiency should create a better life,

158
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:16,640
not sacrifice life itself. Right?

159
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,720
I shouldn't give up on anyone.

160
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:24,450
And no one deserves to be left behind by the times.

161
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,520
Here,

162
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,880
I, Situ Hongtang,

163
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:32,280
apologize to everyone on behalf of Shanshui Group.

164
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,770
What good is an apology?

165
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,800
We want jobs!

166
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:36,480
We need to eat!

167
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,360
We want jobs! We want jobs!

168
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,680
Listen to me. Everyone, quiet down.

169
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:43,840
I've discussed this with the Group's leadership.

170
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,560
Regarding the laid-off miners,

171
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:49,200
the Group will provide free vocational training and career guidance.

172
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:52,280
We'll arrange for you to work at affiliated mines.

173
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,360
Does that mean we won't be laid off?

174
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,440
Yes.

175
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,680
Can we keep mining or not?

176
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,380
Yes. Of course you can.

177
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:04,880
I will personally arrange the takeover of your mines.

178
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:08,320
The pay and safety will be better than here.

179
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:11,480
This is the solution I fought for on your behalf.

180
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:18,800
I will ensure that every villager in Dayang Village has a job.

181
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,160
And food to eat.

182
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,400
No one will be left behind.

183
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,360
I hereby announce...

184
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:29,060
...that Shanshui Group's Security Department is doubling its size.

185
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,720
Raise your hand if you want to sign up.

186
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,800
Is that for real?

187
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,000
I trust them. I'm signing up.

188
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,440
I'll sign up too.

189
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:36,850
I want to sign up.

190
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:41,280
Welcome to Shanshui Group, everyone.
